Description:&nbsp;  
 This repository is in supplementary to the main respository ( https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.15223778 ) of the following study:&nbsp; 
 Hefei Zhang#, Xuhang Li#, Dongyuan Song, Onur Yukselen, Shivani Nanda, Alper Kucukural, Jingyi Jessica Li, Manuel Garber , Albertha J.M. Walhout. Worm Perturb-Seq: massively parallel whole-animal RNAi and RNA-seq. (2025) Nature Communications,&nbsp;in press (# equal contribution, *: correspondng author ) 
  This repository contains only a single file.&nbsp; This file contains the output directory of&nbsp;the EmpirDE parameter optimization and experimental benchmarking. To use it, please unzip the file and move the resulting 'output' folder to the following folder from the  main repository &nbsp; 
   output/ ==&gt;&nbsp; " MetabolicLibrary/2_DE/output/ "&nbsp;  
 Please refer to the  main repository  for more details.&nbsp; 
  Contact:  
  For any questions, please contact Xuhang (Hang) Li at Xuhang.Li@umassmed.edu.&nbsp;

